videos.description: Kevin Durant pumps up the Warriors before their Game 5 showdown with the Raptors.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Misc. (KD hypes up Warriors before Game 5) 2019/06/10

videos.headline: KD hypes up Warriors before Game 5

videos.description: Drake teams up with the Raptors' faithful in belting the Canadian anthem before Game 5 against the Warriors.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Misc. (Drake joins in on ‘Oh Canada’ recital) 2019/06/10

videos.headline: Drake joins in on 'Oh Canada' recital

videos.description: Kevin Durant leaves Scotiabank Arena on crutches after re-injuring his leg during Game 5.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA One-Play (KD leaves arena on crutches) 2019/6/10

videos.headline: KD leaves arena on crutches

videos.description: Klay Thompson says it was deflating seeing Kevin Durant go down but once they got back onto the court, they wanted to win Game 5 for him.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Klay: We did this for KD) 2019/06/10

videos.headline: Klay: We did this for KD

videos.description: Paul Pierce, Michelle Beadle, Jalen Rose and Chauncey Billups struggle making sense of late Raptors' decisions as they lose Game 5 vs. the Warriors 106-105.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (NBA Countdown crew 'shocked' by late Raptors mistakes) 2019/06/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: NBA Countdown crew 'shocked' by late Raptors mistakes

videos.description: Doris Burke tells Scott Van Pelt how the Warriors were able to overcome the loss of Kevin Durant to win Game 5.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Burke: Warriors ‘played like champions’) 2019/6/10 SC SVP

videos.headline: Burke: Warriors 'played like champions'

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith calls out Raptors coach Nick Nurse for calling a timeout after going on a 10-0 run, essentially ending any momentum the team had.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: Nurse 'disrupts his own team’s rhythm') 2019/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stephen A.: Nurse 'disrupts his own team's rhythm'

videos.description: Warriors president of basketball operations Bob Myers holds back tears talking about Kevin Durant hurting his Achilles.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Warriors GM Myers holds back tears talking KD Achilles injury) 2019/06/10

videos.headline: Warriors GM Myers holds back tears talking KD Achilles injury

videos.description: Brian Windhorst reacts to Kevin Durant leaving with an Achillies injury and how it affects the future of the NBA.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Windhorst on Durant’s injury: ‘Entire NBA just changed’) 2019/06/10 ESHEET SVPSC

videos.headline: Windhorst on Durant's injury: 'Entire NBA just changed'

videos.description: Draymond Green joins SVP after the Warriors' Game 5 win over the Raptors to talk about how Kevin Durant's injury impacted the team.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Draymond: KD’s Injury 'took the life out of us') 2019/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Draymond: KD's Injury 'took the life out of us'

videos.description: DeMarcus Cousins reacts very passionately to the Raptors fans cheering when Kevin Durant left the court with an Achilles injury.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Cousins calls fans ‘trash’ for cheering after KD’s injury) 2019/6/10

videos.headline: Cousins calls fans 'trash' for cheering after KD's injury

videos.description: Klay Thompson says it's "just ludicrous" to say the Warriors are better without Kevin Durant, adding that he makes the team "one of the greatest ever."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Press Conference (Klay gets fired up talking about KD’s impact on the Warriors) 2019/6/10

videos.headline: Klay gets fired up talking about KD's impact on the Warriors

videos.description: Rachel Nichols says the Warriors were very emotional after the Game 5 win because they felt for their teammate Kevin Durant after he injured his Achilles.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Nichols: Warriors locker room was very emotional) 2019/06/10 ESHEET SCSVP

videos.headline: Nichols: Warriors' locker room was very emotional

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard was asked why he didn't take the final shot and he laughed then said there were two guys running at him so it would have been tough.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Kawhi laughs when asked why he didn’t take final shot) 2019/06/10

videos.headline: Kawhi laughs when asked why he didn't take final shot

videos.description: Nick Nurse addresses the timeout he called after the Raptors had just gone on a 10-0 run.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Nurse on late timeout: ‘Thought we could use energy push’ ) 2019/6/10

videos.headline: Nurse on late timeout: 'Thought we could use energy push'

videos.description: Jalen Rose expects the Warriors will rally behind the loss of Kevin Durant and give the Raptors too much to handle in Game 6.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Jalen expects Dubs to handle Raptors in Game 6) 2019/6/11 ESHEET GetUp

videos.headline: Jalen expects Dubs to handle Raptors in Game 6

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith explains that Kevin Durant played in Game 5 to prove his dedication to his teammates and the game of basketball.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: KD played to prove his character) 2019/06/11 ESHEET FT

videos.headline: Stephen A.: KD played to prove his character

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith says Raptors coach Nick Nurse calling a timeout late in the 4th quarter changed the momentum and allowed the Warriors to win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A. blames Nurse for Raptors' Game 5 loss) 2019/06/11 ESHEET FT

videos.headline: Stephen A. blames Nurse for Raptors' Game 5 loss

videos.description: Jalen Rose isn't buying people's claims that they are only concerned about Kevin Durant's best interest.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Jalen: Concern about KD’s best interest is ‘phony') 2019/06/11 ESHEET FT

videos.headline: Jalen: Concern about KD's best interest is 'phony'

videos.description: Max Kellerman says that the Raptors fans cheering when Kevin Durant got injured was just a "gut reaction" to the situation.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Max defends Raptors fans after cheering for KD injury) 2019/06/11 ESHEET FT
